{"ja290:0.1":"Jataka ","ja290:0.2":"Tikanipata ","ja290:0.3":"Abbhantaravagga ","ja290:0.4":"10. Silavimamsakajataka ","ja290:1.1":"“Silam kireva kalyanam, ","ja290:1.2":"silam loke anuttaram; ","ja290:1.3":"Passa ghoraviso nago, ","ja290:1.4":"silavati na hannati. ","ja290:2.1":"Soham silam samadissam, ","ja290:2.2":"loke anumatam sivam; ","ja290:2.3":"Ariyavuttisamacaro, ","ja290:2.4":"yena vuccati silava. ","ja290:3.1":"Natinanca piyo hoti, ","ja290:3.2":"mittesu ca virocati; ","ja290:3.3":"Kayassa bheda sugatim, ","ja290:3.4":"upapajjati silava”ti. ","ja290:4.1":"Silavimamsakajatakam dasamam. ","ja290:4.2":"Abbhantaravaggo catuttho. ","ja290:5.1":"Tassuddanam ","ja290:6.1":"Duma kamsavaruttamabyagghamiga, ","ja290:6.2":"Manayo mani salukamavhayano; ","ja290:6.3":"Anusasaniyopi ca macchavaro, ","ja290:6.4":"Manikundalakena kirena dasati. "}